Joseph Y. SAUNDERS, Appellant, v. John W. SNOOK, Warden of U. S. Penitentiary at Atlanta, Georgia, Appellee. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. October 25, 1927. No. 5144. Jos. Y. Saunders, of Atlanta, Ga., in pro. per. J. W. Henley, Asst. U. S. Atty., of Atlanta, Ga., for appellee.

Before WALKER, BRYAN, and POSTER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The order appealed from is affirmed.
